  <mainDescription>&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Solution Description&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Collaborative Application Lifecycle Management streamlines software delivery by:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Coordinating the activities in the software development lifecycle through requirements, analysis, development,&#xD;
        build, test&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Enabling linking and traceability across the artifacts used or produced by team members&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Enabling and enforcing processes that span these activities&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Reporting on progress of the whole&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul>&lt;br />&#xD;
&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Symptoms&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    The following symptoms indicate a need for improvement in lifecycle collaboration:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Low-bandwidth communication, ineffective communication across functions&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        High inconsistency among deliverables&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Disconnected team members&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Team spends a lot of time in status meetings or trying to figure out what needs to be done&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Hand-off problems, miscommunication between functional groups&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        No single repository to share project deliverables&lt;br />&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul>&#xD;
